      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This car is seriously in pristine, like-new condition\u2014it's been babied since day one! It looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot. If you're looking for a total gem that drives like a dream and is completely flawless, this is the one. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
