    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example is mechanically flawless; the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with plates, and the rod bearing service is documented. Power is managed through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The suspension retains its original geometry with fresh bushings throughout, ensuring the telepathic handling these chassis are known for. No pixel degradation, no VANOS rattle, and a completely dry undercarriage. This is a turn-key collector piece for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 46500.0,
