    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true collector\u2019s masterpiece: a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, retaining its deep, mirror-like factory finish with zero imperfections, chips, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any creases or wear, still carrying that distinct new-car scent. Every button, switch, and electronic feature functions flawlessly, and the original high-pile carpets have been protected since day one. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule documented by a complete, chronological folder of service records. With exceptionally low mileage and a chassis that has never seen inclement weather, this is a rare opportunity to own a flawless example of automotive excellence. Includes all original keys, factory manuals, and a bespoke car cover.",
